{"title": "No escape from the boss with Wi-Fi in the sky", "tags": "opinion", "timestamp": "2023-06-18", "content": "Singapore Airlines is giving free unlimited in-flight Wi-Fi to its KrisFlyer members in all cabin classes from July 1. It looks like a savvy move by the airline and a sweet reward for frequent fliers.\nIt also got me wondering. Do we rejoice that work and play can continue unabated in the air? Or regret the loss of a sanctuary in the sky?"}